 regress revpar loyal// Do things change if we control for the competitive revparbysort year: regress revpar comprev loyalstop// because we created some new variables, we want to save this dataset in case we want to use it latersave "data/guestfirst-case-data-data-part-a-new-variables.dta", replace// closes your loglog close// drops all data from Stata's memoryclear